name: Hexamis
description: In this very special episode of Swerve's Bar podcast we do a Q&A session with the talented artist Hexamis who also plays Spitfire in our spin Transformers DnD series.

name: V
description: In this very special episode of Swerve's Bar podcast we do a Q&A session with the talented V who creates amazing animations!

name: Lapis
description: In this special episode of the podcast, we get to interview Lapis of the Arizona Autobots! Come get to know our new friend! You might even get a sneak peak at the upcoming new season of our spin off Transformers DnD series!

name: Highbeam
description: In this special episode of the podcast, we get to interview HighbeamTF! Come get to know our new friend!

name: Celestedoodles
description: A whole new Q&A special! This time we get to interview the talented Celestdoodles!

name: Selt
description: We are back with a brand new Q&A session with two members from the Arizona Autobots! A returning guess, Lapis, and our new guest, Selt! Let's Dive in and get to know our new friend!

name: Cass
description: HERE WE GO! A brand new Q&A session with the fantastic Cass! Be sure to go check them out on Tik-Tok, they make some funny Transformers clips!

name: Lita
description: Elita-1 Army Let's Go! As in today's special Q&A episode we get to sit down and have a blast with Lita!

name: Joe
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented Joe Fiduccia, the owner of the world's only fan-built Age of Extinction replica of Optimus Prime.

name: Travis Artz
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented Travis Artz, the voice of Cyberverse Hot Rod. Go follow Travis! Here are their Socials!

name: Benni Latham
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented Benni Latham, the voice of Dot Malto in Transformers Earthspark.

name: Tiana Camacho
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented Tiana Camacho, the voice of Frenzy in Transformers Earthspark.

name: Jeanne Carr
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented Jeanne Carr, the voice of Blackarachnia in Transformers War For Cybertron.

name: Andy Barnett
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented Andy Barnett, the voice of Rhinox in Transformers War For Cybertron.

name: David Kaye
description: In this exciting Q&A episode we get to talk with the talented David Kaye, the voice of Megatron in Transformers Beast Wars, Megatron in  Transformers Armada and Optimus Prime in Transformers Animated .

name: Lily Flowerdrop
description: Let's get to know some local artist! In this months Q&A we get to interview the wonderful Lily Flowerdrop! Tune in and learn the secrets to making lovely and amazing art!

name: Ryan Miller
description: We get the pleasure of having the talented Ryan Miller on the show! Come join us and meet our new friend who has amazing skills in water colors and making giant monsters!
